OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening for most with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells though a few showers are
OL,8,Fpossible. Turning damp overnight with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain for many, with the
OL,10,Fodd heavier burst possible later.
OL,11,FIncreasingly breezy with gusty
OL,12,Fsoutheasterly winds developing. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA cloudy, cool and
OL,15,Foccasionally wet day with rain or
OL,16,Fshowers. Much of the rain will be
OL,17,Fquite light but heavy and thundery
OL,18,Fdownpours are possible late afternoon.
OL,19,FOccasionally windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
