OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarmer
OL,6,Fon Sunday but breezy and rather cloudy
OL,7,Fwith the odd shower. Hazy sunshine
OL,8,Fpossible at times. Rain overnight,
OL,9,Fclearing to brighter skies on Monday.
OL,10,FSunshine and showers on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
